{"tid":2090202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝手足過去一路嘅堅持","createTime":"2020-07-02T04:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T06:10:21.000Z","uid":152944,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb93396c211b7763a05cd8337661c5f3eeffaaf","tid":2090202,"uid":152944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:56:05.000Z","msg":"當初出警嫂嘅時候 個個親中建制藍絲話暴徒冇啦 玩完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果抗爭依然繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到出緊急法嘅時候 班親中建制藍絲又話暴徒要收皮啦 死硬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果依然繼續Black bloc蒙面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家出蝈安法嘅時候 班親中建制藍絲又話暴徒要坐監啦 終身監禁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果睇吓琴日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依啲失敗嘅政策令到林鄭同政府嘅Legitimacy越嚟越差 最後再推論落去就係影響中共政府嘅Legitimacy 共狗係廢嘅無管治威信 依個政權唔係irreplacable<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以手足堅持呀 大家嘅努力係無白費㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f95ba96ecc603d53f13252d5b264b0595429a46","tid":2090202,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"民族自強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b0da06c6dccdb4a28b3788eb3be818bddcf76f","tid":2090202,"uid":209026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f95ba96ecc603d53f13252d5b264b0595429a46","tid":2090202,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:59:12.000Z","msg":"民族自強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"再唔留言就沉啦"},{"pid":"d52dc92cf18a68353899f2056b110fa23c1c00c7","tid":2090202,"uid":152944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f95ba96ecc603d53f13252d5b264b0595429a46","tid":2090202,"uid":152944,"like":1,